"10年前我個friend 大學major數學<br />\n無數計ga wo<br />\n全部都係背"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T00:56:47.000Z","msg":"先唔好講research level<br />\n單單純死背應該冇可能過考試，起碼要明自己睇緊乜<br />\n好難想像邏輯差可以明ug數學啲推論"},{"pid":"f8ce5052c905536ac1d37f23e32d6466cfa5c8d2","tid":1050083,"uid":41243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:04:03.000Z","msg":"最簡單如果有個人邏輯差到連if同only if都分唔到，仲讀乜數學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a3fb55abe329a25c589f3dd9af287e8d8f7e8e5","tid":1050083,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f8ce5052c905536ac1d37f23e32d6466cfa5c8d2","tid":1050083,"uid":41243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:04:03.000Z","msg":"最簡單如果有個人邏輯差到連if同only if都分唔到，仲讀乜數學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:11:23.000Z","msg":"睇你講咩數學啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eeed0807032ad9872fcd5b53c6fc7839f30339e","tid":1050083,"uid":173852,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"5fb732ae876c1798ecd9b5520065ce82a96e4b07","tid":1050083,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T17:50:17.000Z","msg":"點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:33:04.000Z","msg":"(9up)<br />\n講過朋友講，如果你想一板一眼咁做野，咁簡工程就最岩，但唔好簡數學、物理。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">邏輯要求既係每一步都清清楚楚</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n讀得好數學同物理既人，邏輯唔會差得去邊。但數學同物理要解決既問題，係「未知」的(包括方法同答案)，需要創造力同抽象思維，唔係搬字過紙就得。<br />\n<br />\n相反，工程既問題係「已知」的，按步就班，用既有既知識解決，通常無大問題。<br />\n當然，落手做一定有好多麻煩野既，但通常都係經驗問題，唔洗要你諗一個前無古人既問題去搞掂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3facbf0d56e96d2fbe1a24983d1b12f01d7de221","tid":1050083,"uid":92278,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:36:36.000Z","msg":"數學好=自閉仔"},{"pid":"7f0b91d611e84c57a3d4f411bc8cc0fce7130133","tid":1050083,"uid":214784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:39:53.000Z","msg":"truth"},{"pid":"3aef6bc6fcd23fe9fe455e7b6367f109c0d055a5","tid":1050083,"uid":87339,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8c19a1d0f776aa555c1543cd6ce4c6219900532","tid":1050083,"uid":142878,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"6b1b95a49a6ff69610710ca4be6a66f9cf3b7999","tid":1050083,"uid":189150,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3bfe3b5e0c695a8811ef9cbf5a44743ed06c6048","tid":1050083,"uid":66324,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T23:54:46.000Z","msg":"邏輯好係咪一定數學好? 唔係<br />\n數學好係咪一定邏輯好? 亦都唔係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T23:57:25.000Z","msg":"如果講中小學數 根本無關係<br />\n中學數學既邏輯 ＝ common sense<br />\n大學讀數先要求邏輯好"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T00:01:02.000Z","msg":"10年前我個friend 大學major數學<br />\n無數計ga wo<br />\n全部都係背"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:51:30.000Z","msg":"real analysis你背畀我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503f6423b8cfe507f7556bd71467ca0628aeeb43","tid":1050083,"uid":126100,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:52:39.000Z","msg":"IT code dog 一定 logic 好"},{"pid":"dc6e3e87481df17570d233cd889d19bfe299526d","tid":1050083,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:57:16.000Z","msg":"樓主大學讀乜，三科（cs，math, phil) 都會讀邏輯囉，咁你點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a38e5860c5c0f48f303903df2250fed1de072d","tid":1050083,"uid":189150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5fb80d5b5e51cdefa032e2693a2390056afa4d00","tid":1050083,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8c19a1d0f776aa555c1543cd6ce4c6219900532","tid":1050083,"uid